{
  "name": "Breath of Mist Haze",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Bukijutsu.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You begin to collect and manifest Illusionary chakra until it radiate off of your weapon similar to that of a mist. The chakra begins to take the same consistency as a thick haze that makes it difficult to see through.</p><p>You generate this haze centered on you that expands outward up to 15 feet and goes around corners. This haze follows you and cannot be blown away by strong winds. Select one hostile creature you can see when you cast this jutsu. This creature cannot see through this haze and you are treated as being fully obscured visually against them. Creatures, creatures attacks and jutsu can still pass through this haze, entering and/or exiting it.</p><p>The first time each turn you would make an attack or cast a jutsu while maintaining this jutsu, your Weapons or Taijutsu's critical threat range is increased by +1.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above C-Rank increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the number of creatures you can target with this jutsu by +1. </p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
